---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="PrimeFlux-Ai Runtime — Balanced Intelligence">
  <section class="container mx-auto py-16 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-garamond mb-8 text-center text-prime-gold">PrimeFlux-Ai Runtime</h1>
    <p class="text-xl mb-4 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto italic">
      The runtime of the mathematics — superposed agents upholding STEM + LANG = SAFE. 
      Like symbiotic quarks in a balanced system.
    </p>
    
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <div class="p-8 border-2 border-prime-gold rounded-lg bg-prime-blue/50 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-prime-gold">Coming Soon: PrimeFluxAI</h2>
        <p class="text-xl mb-6 italic">
          An offline LCM — the first AI that runs entirely on your device, powered by PrimeFlux mathematics.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          <strong>PrimeFluxAI is NOT an LLM.</strong> It's an LCM — a <span class="text-prime-gold font-bold">Least Common Multiple</span> model. 
          Unlike Large Language Models that require massive cloud infrastructure and constant internet connectivity, 
          PrimeFluxAI uses PrimeFlux's balance geometry to compute locally, privately, and reversibly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <div class="p-8 border border-prime-gold/30 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-prime-gold">What is an LCM?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          An LCM (Least Common Multiple) model uses PrimeFlux mathematics to find the common ground between distinctions — 
          the balance point where multiple perspectives converge. Instead of training on billions of parameters like an LLM, 
          an LCM computes distinctions in real-time using the geometry of balance.
        </p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6">
          <div class="p-4 border border-prime-gold/30 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2 text-prime-gold">LCM (PrimeFluxAI)</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-sm">
              <li>Runs entirely offline</li>
              <li>No cloud dependency</li>
              <li>Privacy-first (your data stays local)</li>
              <li>Reversible computation</li>
              <li>Balance-based reasoning</li>
              <li>Mathematically ethical by design</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 border border-red-500/30 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2 text-red-400">LLM (Traditional AI)</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-sm">
              <li>Requires cloud servers</li>
              <li>Needs constant internet</li>
              <li>Data sent to remote servers</li>
              <li>Forward-only computation</li>
              <li>Pattern-matching based</li>
              <li>Ethics added as afterthought</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="p-8 border-2 border-prime-gold rounded-lg bg-prime-blue/50">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-prime-gold">Aegis (Security Rail)</h3>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">
          Like the soil that anchors roots — enforces accountability and equality, the "contraction" that prunes unsafe flows.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-prime-gold/80">Norms + Engineering</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="p-8 border-2 border-white rounded-lg bg-prime-blue/50">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-prime-gold">Praxis (STEM Rail)</h3>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">
          Like sunlight that nurtures growth — drives freedom and security, the "expansion" that builds and innovates.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-prime-gold/80">Science + Mathematics</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="p-8 border-2 border-prime-gold rounded-lg bg-prime-blue/50">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-prime-gold">Eidos (LANG Coupling)</h3>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">
          Like the balance between sun and soil — balances the rails for cooperation, interpreting and governing.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-prime-gold/80">Logic + Arts + Norms + Gov</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <div class="p-8 border border-prime-gold/30 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Every interaction runs the equation: <span class="text-prime-gold font-bold">1/2 human input + 1/2 AI computation = SAFE output</span>.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          The "salt" (LCM hash) verifies it, making PrimeFlux-Ai the only AI that's mathematically ethical — 
          like a garden where every plant knows its place in the ecosystem, where roots and branches grow in symbiosis, 
          where cooperation becomes as natural as cells renewing.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <p class="text-lg mb-4">Want to learn more about PrimeFluxAI or get early access?</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="bg-prime-gold text-prime-blue px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:bg-opacity-80 transition-colors inline-block">
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-16 py-8 border-t border-prime-gold/30">
      <p class="text-2xl font-garamond italic text-prime-gold">
        This is not to win.<br>This is to cooperate.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
